@dev Queries the current price for a token pair.
@param baseToken The base token.
@param quoteToken The quote token.
@return price The present market price.

@dev Calculates the trading depth available for a token pair.
@param baseToken The base token.
@param quoteToken The quote token.
@return depth Available trading depth for the base token.

@dev Adds liquidity to a liquidity pool.
@param tokenA The first token in the pool.
@param tokenB The second token in the pool.
@param amountA The quantity of the first token.
@param amountB The quantity of the second token.
@param acceptedSlippage Maximum acceptable slippage.
@param provider Address of the liquidity provider.
@param deadline Transaction deadline.
@return newAmountA Amount of token A added.
@return newAmountB Amount of token B added.

@dev Redeems liquidity tokens for underlying assets.
@param tokenA The first token in the pool.
@param tokenB The second token in the pool.
@param desiredAmountTokenA Desired amount of the first token.
@param desiredAmountTokenB Desired amount of the second token.
@param lpTokenQty Quantity of liquidity tokens.
@param recipient Recipient of the withdrawn assets.
@param deadline Transaction deadline.
@param acceptedSlippage Maximum acceptable slippage.
@return unredeemedLpTokens Remaining unredeemed liquidity tokens.

@dev Executes a token swap.
@param path Sequence of tokens to be swapped.
@param desiredAmountOut Desired amount of the final token.
@param maxPrice Maximum acceptable price across the token pairs in the path.
@param recipient Address to receive the final tokens.
@param routingAgent Agent responsible for routing the swap.
@param deadline Transaction deadline.
@return actualAmountOut Actual amount of tokens received.
@return amountInUsed Tokens spent for the swap.

@dev Computes input and output quantities for a token swap.
@param path Sequence of tokens to be swapped.
@return amountInRequired Required amount of initial tokens.
@return amountOutMax Maximum amount of final tokens to be received.
